## Investigation Steps

1. Identify the new account.
2. Verify who created it.
3. Confirm whether it was authorized.
4. Check if the account was added to privileged groups.
5. Review subsequent login activity.

---

## Conclusion

Unauthorized account creation is a common persistence technique used by attackers after compromising a system.
